cellularData

Class CSVReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • cellularData.CSVReader

  • public class CSVReader
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will take a CSV file as a parameter then separate and store the information of the file. It then has methods to return a list of countries in the data, the table of data, the years of the data, and the total years of data.
    Author:
    Zach Rooney
